* '''Use easy words''' and '''shorter sentences''' so people who speak little [[English language|English]] may easily read them.
* '''Write good pages with care.''' The best [[encyclopedia]] pages have useful information. They are also carefully written.
* '''Use the pages to learn''' and '''teach.''' These pages can tell things to people who speak little English.  You can also use them to [[m:How_to_start_a_new_Wikipedia|make a Wikipedia]] to help other people, if you change the words to your own language.

